intro: Break the blocks or break her heart.
description:
Grab your paddle and get ready to aim, bounce, and break your way to a gorgeous reveal. Every hit brings you closer to what’s hidden behind and the satisfaction of a perfect clear has never looked this good.

Keep your focus, control your shots, and watch as the tension builds with every block you destroy. But be careful… miss too many, and the moment might slip away.

Features:
- 32 stunning girls waiting to be revealed
- Sensual music and satisfying effects
- Addictive arcade-style gameplay
- A treat for your eyes

Keep your balls in play, and break through to your reward.
